        </fig>
        <lg>
            <l n="1">The <beast>Microbe</beast> is so very small</l>
            <l n="2">You cannot make him out at all,</l>
            <l n="3">But many sanguine people hope</l>
            <l n="4">To see him through a microscope.</l>
            <l n="5">His jointed tongue that lies beneath</l>
            <l n="6">A hundred curious rows of teeth;</l>
            <l n="7">His seven tufted tails with lots</l>
            <l n="8">Of lovely pink and purple spots,</l>
        </lg>
        <pgNum n="248">[248]</pgNum>
    </pg>
